{"tid":1029831,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲人連住邊都要吹大","createTime":"2019-02-20T13:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T21:17:17.000Z","uid":860,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb0207dc280e21596ae1875af08bc41f3be9a30","tid":1029831,"uid":860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，上星期同個朋友行完街，咁又有啲野比佢，咁佢就車我返屋企拎，返到上屋企見到阿妹同啲大學同學係屋企食緊野，咁時間仲早我同我朋友都係屋企一齊吹下水咁<br />\n咁我阿妹同3個同學，2女1男，個男我聽佢講野都聽得出佢係咁Show off,咁係女同學面前認叻都正常嘅<br />\n咁見咁上下我朋友就話不如食糖水，咁我問埋阿妹一唔一齊，咁佢又叫埋啲同學<br />\n好啦，咁一齊坐我朋友車落旺角，點知間間都好多人，咁我朋友就話可以買上佢屋企，話如果夜可以車返大家出去搭車<br />\n咁啲同學仔當然問下住邊，咁我朋友就講左句樂富，我就話廣播道就廣播道啦，點知我阿妹同佢2個女同學都即刻指住個男同學，咪姐係你鄰居<br />\n我朋友就問下佢住邊到咁啦，個男同學就話都係廣播道咁上下，可能岩岩識唔講都正常<br />\n就去到我朋友屋企個時，我朋友先記得得一個ps4手製，咁咪問下男同學有無，有就去佢屋企攞埋，點知男同學就話佢屋企遠唔方便，我已經心諗廣播道有幾大，仲要有車，點知問下問下先知，原來男同學住廣播道對面富強苑<br />\n見到我阿妹同佢啲同學忍住笑我大概估到咩事，就即刻話，都好近姐，不如食糖水先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實住邊到真係要咁都呃人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry有啲長，但真係太深刻"},{"pid":"167e1e3dc27804cc514a5641e4e29ef2b7898fcb","tid":1029831,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"562961c436a459a988342f99b0eb03c40e3ee251","tid":1029831,"uid":16624,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"你都幾好心機"},{"pid":"1972d29c3c4341d9f52f7fee79e57321164190dd","tid":1029831,"uid":232594,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"勵志故事結尾：然後男同學下年就搬左去廣播道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ea12b00d6309926ee0b09c675fe49aaddc658a","tid":1029831,"uid":88491,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"見識唔小呢d人，佢地應該有病態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de619751b3d06c03210d018758c858c02f367c5","tid":1029831,"uid":68457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"88ea12b00d6309926ee0b09c675fe49aaddc658a","tid":1029831,"uid":88491,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"見識唔小呢d人，佢地應該有病態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"鍾意到處吹噓嘅人到大個通常都會後悔, 覺得自己好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2131861fccf41a69977d389c0512630b59231b83","tid":1029831,"uid":181697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"當你係的士佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e24cb2881a3b34870fb9ea207d42896f7eac3db","tid":1029831,"uid":208376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"仲以為住樂富村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6f31dcd1669d2b3867fead5cf9a837ebfca13c","tid":1029831,"uid":4139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"柒到出煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df69835167e27f46326d4138a33071f961447c7f","tid":1029831,"uid":141782,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"以前識得有個人話自己住西隧口嗰邊<br />\n個個以為佢住九龍站<br />\n原來深水埗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有個話自己住又一城附近<br />\n原來係石硤尾d 屋邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36cbf39f23d66a734264780bf43205646e12fbf","tid":1029831,"uid":177004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"我親戚，話嫁咗會搬去黃埔花園，<br />\n點知係太子唐樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f215a4132a63888b237db06853e809204a987b","tid":1029831,"uid":213636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"識人話住popcorn點知係善明邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912e6dbe576ebe63350db6a2efeb31775d94fb31","tid":1029831,"uid":860,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c6f31dcd1669d2b3867fead5cf9a837ebfca13c","tid":1029831,"uid":4139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"柒到出煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T19:37:51.000Z","msg":"個下我都覺得柒連笑都廢事，始終又唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94e8ca67af9ef33e38fb852fcdb01f0cecf9a6c","tid":1029831,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T20:12:29.000Z","msg":"原來咁自卑嘅人都有"},{"pid":"4b4b4a034e283061eafaa7f9aeca44c30499df0e","tid":1029831,"uid":228131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T20:29:38.000Z","msg":"我姑媽話自己住世界花園，但其實住新田圍"},{"pid":"aa39500996cc666ec2d65751c6b3d56c140ccdc7","tid":1029831,"uid":17232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T20:51:20.000Z","msg":"咁我朋友就講左句樂富，<span style=\"color: red;\">我就話廣播道就廣播道啦</span><br />\n<br />\n純粹想問吓，點解要講句咁嘅野？"},{"pid":"db21a2a9db49853e8ea9bdbca9ec3a7e3e49375f","tid":1029831,"uid":84104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse